---
import LabLayout from '../layouts/LabLayout.astro';
---

<LabLayout title="Join — Jungbluth Lab">
  <br />
  <h1 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Joining the Lab</h1>

  <div class="mt-8 prose prose-gray max-w-none">
    <p>We would love to hear from you if your interests align with the lab.</p>

    <br />
    <p>Right now we accept students from SFSU.</p>

    <br />
    <h2>Graduate Students</h2>
    <p>We normally accept Master's students to work on projects towards earning an M.S. degree in the <a href="https://biology.sfsu.edu/graduate/integrative" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong>Integrative Biology</strong></a> or <a href="https://cs.sfsu.edu/grads/graduate-program" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong>Computer Science</strong></a> departments. SFSU does not currently have a PhD program for marine science, but we are open to co-advising PhD students from other universities.</p>

    <br />
    <h2>Research Assistants &amp; Volunteers</h2>
    <p>Graduate and undergraduate research assistants or volunteers seeking experience in the marine sciences are encouraged to reach out — we can always use an extra hand in the lab or field.</p>

    <br />
    <h2>Post-doctoral Scholars</h2>
    <p>We would be happy to discuss opportunities and support fellowship application efforts.</p>
    <br />

    <hr />

    <p>Please contact us directly by sending an email to either Sean or Michelle at the addresses below.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
    <div class="rounded-lg bg-michelle-50 border border-michelle-200 p-6">
      <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Michelle Jungbluth, PhD</h3>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-michelle-700">Oceanographer, Zooplankton and Food Web Ecologist</p>
      <div class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-700">
        <p>mjungbluth at sfsu dot edu</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-lg bg-sean-50 border border-sean-200 p-6">
      <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Sean Jungbluth, PhD</h3>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-sean-700">Oceanographer, Microbial Ecologist, and Computational Biologist</p>
      <div class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
        <p class="text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">General Inquiries</p>
        <p>seanj dot lab at gmail dot com</p>
        <p class="text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider mt-2">SFSU-specific Inquiries</p>
        <p>sjungbluth at sfsu dot edu</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</LabLayout>
